p: Top fifteen human protein targets were obtained for each of the bioactives from SwissTargetPrediction, listed in Supplementary Table S4. Human protein targets for SARS-CoV-2 were obtained from the literature survey, also summarized in Supplementary Table S4. Pathway enrichment analysis was performed for both the HMP bioactive targets and the SARS-CoV-2 targets using the Enrichr.
